Final  
In Neckar Stadion (Stuttgart)
25-05-88 PSV Eindhoven (Ned)            0-0 Benfica (Por)       [aet, 6-5 pen]
EINDHOVEN: Hans van Breukelen; Eric Gerets (c), Ivan Nielsen, Ronald Koeman, Jan Heintze, 
           Berry van Aerle, Gerald Vanenburg, Edward Linskens, Soren Lerby, Willem Kieft, 
           Hans Gillhaus (Anton Jannsen 107)
           COACH: Guus Hiddink
